439→ * pending_auth. The EVENT calls http::post to the real test server's
440→ * evaluate endpoint, enabling true E2E testing of the async evaluation flow.
441→ *
442→ * Call this in beforeAll after the test server has booted.
443→ */
444→export async function wireIntentEvaluationEvent(
